{"tid":1098471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果日報的免費訂閱其實背後做緊乜？","createTime":"2019-04-09T05:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T21:10:47.000Z","uid":38794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf62d49dcc7992adc984bed12a56dbcda702e1a","tid":1098471,"uid":38794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報今天都好難靠賣紙的全版廣告救命，所以大搞 online(其實一直都搞），今次要member subscription 方式來行，估計末來會變收費/部分收費。<br />\n<br />\n但佢呢個階段好怪<br />\n4月10日開始改文章要login 看？<br />\n4 月10日前訂閱係free<br />\n4月10日開始若未login 就會show,login 及免費登記的畫面叫人登入 = 都係free<br />\n<br />\n重點<br />\n1. 幾時登記都係free?<br />\n2. 改版rc為要login 才可看文章<br />\n3. 用email 也可reg account ,不一定要電話<br />\n4 . seo 必定因為有member wall 而轉差<br />\n5. fb 看到文章彈login screen 再login ?<br />\n<br />\n搞完一堆野，其實同之前有唔同嗎？彈login 才可看，變相少左好多 online ads 顯示次數，呢個會員制真係行得通嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係改收費版，但做新聞唔係做專欄，呢個唔睇就睇下一間，反正獨家新聞最多都係獨一兩個鐘就俾01 引用吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab9f5d122b38c0ada5e97a553ff428f83bc797a","tid":1098471,"uid":61280,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買賣Database養命，等睇同HKTV合併！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"26f588829e9ceb500e300fd720fff3a9e19d9d3c","tid":1098471,"uid":163081,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:47:46.000Z","msg":"佢唔會一直免費落去啦，同埋依家咁多content farm, fake news，可能係想有質素讀者買有質素新聞。當然蘋果日報本身有冇質素就大家自有定論&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c5d13aa378e984b4d29d78ee0de1b870ac4e3795","tid":1098471,"uid":38794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"賣data 會損品牌，死得仲快。"},{"pid":"f7fb413f0f3f9dde7a5dd207a520b353057a7142","tid":1098471,"u